    <p class="muted" style="margin:0 0 12px;">
      Cookies are small files stored on your device. Some are required for site functionality; others help with advertising or analytics.
    </p>

    <h2 style="margin: 14px 0 8px;">Essential cookies</h2>
    <p class="muted" style="margin:0;">
